<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Internal Server Error</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff6b6b;
            --secondary-color: #feca57;
            --text-color: #ffffff;
            --background-start: #1a1a1a;
            --background-end: #0f0f0f;
            --container-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --shadow-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--background-start), var(--background-end));
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .error-container {
            padding: 60px 40px;
            background: var(--container-bg);
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px var(--shadow-color);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -20px;
            left: -20px;
            width: 120%;
            height: 120%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--primary-color) 0%, transparent 60%);
            opacity: 0.05;
            z-index: -1;
            animation: pulse-glow 4s infinite ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 10rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .error-description {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0.7;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .home-btn, .retry-btn {
            padding: 14px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .home-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));
            color: #1a1a1a;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .home-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .retry-btn {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-color);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .retry-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse-glow {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .error-container {
                padding: 40px 25px;
            }
            .error-actions {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-code">500</div>
        <h1 class="error-message">Internal Server Error</h1>
        <p class="error-description">
            We are experiencing an issue on our servers. Our team has been notified and is working hard to resolve it. Thank you for your patience.
        </p>
        <div class="error-actions">
            <a href="/home" class="home-btn">Go to Homepage</a>
            <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="retry-btn">Try Again</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>